$ SQL Developer: View -> Snippets

The menu *View -> Snippets* allows to define «snippets» (text fragments) that can be dragged onto the 
→ development/Software/Oracle-SQL-Developer/GUI/SQL-Worksheet[SQL worksheet].

sa:
  The menus
    • → development/Software/Oracle-SQL-Developer/GUI/menu/Tools/Preferences/Database/SQL-Editor-Code-Templates[Tools -> Preferences -> Database -> SQL Editor Code Templates]
    • → development/Software/Oracle-SQL-Developer/GUI/menu/Tools/Preferences/Shortcut-Keys[Tools -> Preferences -> Shortcut Keys]
